The following is captured in the grid state:


* [Aggregation Functions](ag-mcp://article/aggregation) (column state)
* [Opened Column Groups](ag-mcp://article/column-groups)
* [Column Order](ag-mcp://article/column-moving) (column state)
* [Pinned Columns](ag-mcp://article/column-pinning) (column state)
